# Routes Rules

## Route Structure Overview

### App Router Organization
- **Next.js 15 App Router** for modern routing
- **Role-based route** organization
- **Protected routes** with middleware
- **Public routes** for general access

## Route Categories

### 1. Authentication Routes
**Base path: `/auth`**

#### Login Routes
- `/auth/login` - Admin login page
- `/auth/signup` - Admin registration page
- `/auth/forgot-password` - Password reset request
- `/auth/forgot-password/otp` - Password reset OTP verification

#### Route Protection
- **Public access** for login/signup
- **Redirect logic** for authenticated users
- **Role-based** redirects after authentication
- **Error handling** for invalid credentials

### 2. Admin Routes
**Base path: `/admin`**

#### Onboarding Routes
- `/admin/onboard/` - Onboarding landing page
- `/admin/onboard/add-org` - Organization creation
- `/admin/onboard/processing` - Approval pending status

#### Dashboard Routes
- `/admin/dashboard/elections` - Main elections dashboard
- `/admin/dashboard/elections/create` - Create new election
- `/admin/dashboard/tickets` - Support tickets management

#### Election Setup Routes
**Base path: `/admin/dashboard/elections/[id]/setup`**

- `/admin/dashboard/elections/[id]/setup/scope` - Voting scope setup
- `/admin/dashboard/elections/[id]/setup/party` - Party management
- `/admin/dashboard/elections/[id]/setup/voter` - Voter registration
- `/admin/dashboard/elections/[id]/setup/position` - Position definition
- `/admin/dashboard/elections/[id]/setup/candidates` - Candidate management

#### Election Management Routes
**Base path: `/admin/dashboard/elections/[id]/manage`**

- `/admin/dashboard/elections/[id]/manage/ballot-preview` - Ballot customization
- `/admin/dashboard/elections/[id]/manage/email-send` - Email distribution
- `/admin/dashboard/elections/[id]/manage/live-dashboard` - Real-time monitoring
- `/admin/dashboard/elections/[id]/manage/2fa-settings` - 2FA method selection

#### Route Protection
- **Admin authentication** required
- **Organization approval** check
- **Election ownership** validation
- **Session validation** on each request

### 3. SuperAdmin Routes
**Base path: `/superadmin`**

#### Dashboard Routes
- `/superadmin/dashboard` - Main dashboard with sidebar navigation
- `/superadmin/dashboard/org-request` - Organization approval
- `/superadmin/dashboard/elections` - Election oversight
- `/superadmin/dashboard/tickets` - Support ticket management
- `/superadmin/dashboard/audits` - System audit logs
- `/superadmin/dashboard/survey-form` - Survey management

#### Route Protection
- **SuperAdmin authentication** required
- **Global access** to all organizations
- **System-wide** permissions
- **Audit logging** for all actions

### 4. Voter Routes
**Base path: `/voter`**

#### Authentication Routes
- `/voter/login` - Voter code entry
- `/voter/login/2fa-email` - Email 2FA verification
- `/voter/login/2fa-otp` - OTP 2FA verification
- `/voter/login/2fa-text` - SMS 2FA verification
- `/voter/login/2fa-passphrase` - Passphrase 2FA verification

#### Election Routes
- `/voter/election-status` - Election status check
- `/voter/election-terms-conditions` - Terms and conditions
- `/voter/ballot-form` - Voting interface
- `/voter/receipt` - Vote receipt
- `/voter/survey-form` - Post-vote survey
- `/voter/live-dashboard` - Live results (requires authentication)

#### Route Protection
- **Voter code** validation required
- **2FA completion** check
- **Election-specific** access control
- **Session-based** authentication

### 5. Public Routes
**Base path: `/` and `/public`**

#### Landing Pages
- `/` - Main landing page
- `/public/about-us` - About page
- `/public/contact` - Contact page

#### Route Protection
- **Public access** allowed
- **No authentication** required
- **SEO optimization** for public pages
- **Performance optimization** for public access

## Route Protection Rules

### Middleware Implementation
- **Next.js middleware** for route protection
- **Role-based** access control
- **Session validation** on each request
- **Automatic redirects** for unauthorized access

### Authentication Checks
- **Session existence** validation
- **Role verification** for protected routes
- **Organization approval** status check
- **Election access** permissions

### Error Handling
- **404 pages** for invalid routes
- **Unauthorized** redirects
- **Error boundaries** for route errors
- **Graceful degradation** for route failures

## Route Organization Principles

### 1. Role Separation
- **Clear separation** between user types
- **No cross-role** route access
- **Isolated navigation** for each role
- **Role-specific** layouts and components

### 2. Nested Routing
- **Logical grouping** of related routes
- **Dynamic segments** for IDs and parameters
- **Consistent URL** patterns
- **SEO-friendly** route structure

### 3. Route Naming
- **Descriptive names** for all routes
- **Consistent naming** conventions
- **URL-friendly** route names
- **Clear hierarchy** in route structure

