## Route Parameters

### Dynamic Segments
- `[id]` - Election ID
- `[scopeId]` - Voting scope ID
- `[partyId]` - Party ID
- `[voterId]` - Voter ID
- `[positionId]` - Position ID
- `[candidateId]` - Candidate ID
- `[ticketId]` - Support ticket ID

### Query Parameters
- `status` - Filter by status
- `page` - Pagination
- `limit` - Results per page
- `search` - Search term
- `sort` - Sort order

